        {
          "renderType": "rich-text",
          "tag": "h2",
          "content": "What is LaterCon?"
        },
        {
          "renderType": "rich-text",
          "tag": "p",
          "content": "LaterCon is a free educational one-day event run annually and virtually by Later (an all-in-one social media marketing platform) to help small business owners learn how to grow their brand on social media."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "renderType": "container",
