          "richTextStyles": true,
          "content": [
            {
              "renderType": "rich-text",
              "tag": "h2",
              "content": "The Project"
            },
            {
              "renderType": "rich-text",
              "tag": "p",
              "content": "Develop a landing page on later.com to promote and drive sign-ups to LaterCon."
            },
            {
              "renderType": "rich-text",
              "tag": "h3",
              "content": "The Brief"
            },
            {
              "renderType": "rich-text",
              "tag": "h4",
              "content": "Context"
            },
            {
              "renderType": "rich-text",
              "tag": "p",
              "content": "LaterCon is organized by Later's content marketing team. After months long planning and preparation they were looking to have a landing page created to announce and promote it. The Creative Director finalized a custom art direction the month before and was in the process of completing the landing page visual design, which left a timeline of a little over two weeks to complete development. Expectations were also high for this year's LaterCon as the previous year saw a 60 percent increase in sign-up and attendance numbers. The marketing team wasn't expecting to replicate 2020 success as the pandemic played a unique role in this, but set ambitious targets nonetheless."
            },
            {
              "renderType": "rich-text",
              "tag": "h4",
              "content": "Goals"
            },
            {
              "renderType": "rich-text",
              "tag": "ul",
              "content": [
                {
                  "tag": "li",
                  "content": "Contribute to overall goal of achieving 60,000 sign-ups amongst all channels (web, social and paid ads)"
                },
                {
                  "tag": "li",
                  "content": "Get 100,000 unique page views"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "renderType": "rich-text",
              "tag": "h4",
              "content": "Requirements"
            },
            {
              "renderType": "rich-text",
              "tag": "ul",
              "content": [
                {
                  "tag": "li",
                  "content": "Include prominent calls-to-action encouraging visitors to register"
                },
                {
                  "tag": "li",
                  "content": "Launch by August 24th"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
