          "richTextStyles": true,
          "content": [
            {
              "renderType": "rich-text",
              "tag": "p",
              "content": "Although stakeholders were pleased with how the page turned out, there were some things we didn't get. The Creative Director was hoping for a mouseover distort of the LaterCon logo in the hero section. A combination of time and performance constraints resulted in a compromise. The effect required a large library and page speed was already in the orange. We opted for a smaller library and a simpler effect&ndash;clicking the cursor icon changes svg paths to simulate a morphing effect. We also encountered a significant hiccup the day before the event&ndash;the post-event version was pushed live. For about an hour registration links were disabled. This was a lesson to draft pull requests and better communicate with team members about time sensitive launches."
            }
          ]
