            {
              "renderType": "rich-text",
              "tag": "p",
              "content": [
                {
                  "content": "Two weeks after launching the landing page, the Demand Generation Director and Creative Project Manager wanted to better support event sign-ups. A quarter of the sign-up goal had been reached but there were only three weeks left. They settled on a homepage interstitial promoting the event. Although they'd already decided on a popup, we mocked up another option&ndash;a banner in the middle of the homepage as entry popups are quite intrusive and there are "
                },
