                  "tag": "a",
                  "link": "https://developers.google.com/search/docs/appearance/avoid-intrusive-interstitials",
                  "content": "SEO penalties"
                },
                {
                  "content": " associated with using them on mobile (unless they're mandatory). The interstitial design won, but we only displayed it in viewports greater than 1000 pixels."
                }
              ]
            }
